These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-1::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: rock, indie
There 2 different types of food: broccoli, spinach
The people have 2 different hobbies: board-games, chess
There are 2 different nationalities: japanese, chinese
1. the japanese is not to the right of the person eating spinach##8
2. the person eating spinach is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##5
3. the fan of rock is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |
| Music-Genre      | indie     | rock      |
| Food          | spinach | broccoli    |
| Hobby         | chess   | board-games |
| Nationality   | japanese  | chinese      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, iced-tea
The people have 2 different hobbies: filmmaking, woodworking
There are 2 different nationalities: indian, pakistani
2 different pets are kept: pony, bird
1. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far right##1
2. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is somewhere to the left of the indian##5
3. the pakistani is not to the right of the indian##8
4. the owner of the pony is not the person who's hobby is woodworking##6

.:: Answer ::.
|             |         1          |      2      |
| Beverage    | almond-milk        | iced-tea    |
| Hobby       | filmmaking         | woodworking |
| Nationality         | pakistani | indian   |
| Pet   | pony               | bird  |

