There 2 different types of food: plum, nectarine
There are 2 different favourite colors: aquamarine, emerald
2 different pets are kept: cat, ferret
1. the person who likes aquamarine is in an odd position##4
2. the person who likes emerald is not to the right of the owner of the ferret##8
3. the person eating plum is somewhere to the left of the person watching thriller movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |
| Movie-Genre   | epic       | thriller |
| Food   | plum       | nectarine    |
| Color   | aquamarine | emerald |
| Pet           | cat        | ferret   |

